	<ThingDef ParentName="BIE_UltratechQuestOnlyCombatImplantBase">
		<defName>BIE_SpacerPlasmaClawCombatModule</defName>
		<label>plasmaclaw combat module</label>
		<description>An arm-like device with a built-in ranged or melee weapon, usually installed onto a person’s upper torso. It consists of two main segments, one for storing and\or producing the necessary ammunition and\or energy and a second one that connects to the user’s arm.  It can function without an arm to connect to, but it greatly benefits from having access to a functional biological or artificial limb. It is not precise enough to be used as a proper arm replacement, though it can function as a useful, if not a bit unwieldy, “extra” arm.\n\nA maximum of two modules can be installed onto a person, a primary module that usually connects to the subject’s dominant arm and a secondary module that connects to the other one. Some modules require to take up both “slots” in order to be usable.\n\nImplants like these tend to be given to high-ranking spacer as well as ultratech-era soldiers and mercenaries. There have been reports of similarly-functioning archotech artifacts being utilized by unknown individuals, but their validity is yet to be confirmed.\n\nThis particular model is equipped with a power claw modified to function similarly to a plasmasword and takes up one “slot”.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks>
			<RecipeDef>InstallBIE_SpacerPlasmaClawCombatModulePrimary</RecipeDef>
			<RecipeDef>InstallBIE_SpacerPlasmaClawCombatModuleSecondary</RecipeDef>
			<ThingDef>MeleeWeapon_PlasmaSword</ThingDef>
		</descriptionHyperlinks>
		<thingSetMakerTags>
			<li>RewardStandardHighFreq</li>
		</thingSetMakerTags>
		<statBases>
			<Mass>5</Mass>
		</statBases>
	</ThingDef>

